STATE EX REL. FANT
v.
SLOAN. 2017-1808 Supreme Court of Ohio. March 14, 2018

CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

MERIT DECISIONS WITHOUT OPINIONS

In Procedendo, Mandamus, Habeas Corpus, and Prohibition. On respondent's motion to dismiss. Motion granted. Cause dismissed. O'Connor, C.J., and O'Donnell, Kennedy, French, Fischer, and DeWine, JJ., concur. DeGenaro, J., not participating.
